We want to send you roses... in the form of intoxicating @kaifragrance products 🌹 We're doing a giveaway with @kaifragrance so you and a friend can enter to win a package of bodycare in our favorite Kai scent - rose.

You'll be getting the following: candle, fragrance duo, body glow, body buffer (loved by Rose Inc. Founder, @rosiehw!), hand cream, body butter, perfume oil, eau de parfum, body lotion, body wash, and deodorant.

To enter, all you have to do is:
-Follow both @roseinc and @kaifragrance
-Tag a friend (or more!) in the comments below (each tag is worth 1 entry)

Both you and your friend must be following both @roseinc and @kaifragrance to win. Contest ends Friday, December 20 at 9AM PST. Winners will be chosen & announced on Instagram stories. Eligible only in US. Must be 13+ to enter. This post is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with, Instagram.
